## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [gpdhc1-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Increased levels of malate in mutant (close to twice that in wildtype). Significant decrease in citrate levels and oxaloacetate.
   - [gpdhc1-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Lower germination rates when grown on plates containing ABA and salt.
   - [gpdhc1-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;No aberrant phenotype when grown under normal conditions; except a slightly earlier flowering initiation.
   - [gpdhc1-2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Increased levels of malate in mutant (close to twice that in wildtype). Significant decrease in citrate levels and oxaloacetate.
   - [gpdhc1-2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Lower germination rates when grown on plates containing ABA and salt.
   - [gpdhc1-2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;No aberrant phenotype when grown under normal conditions; except a slightly earlier flowering initiation.
